  "message": "feat(conformance): add run_id and scenario_id fields to E2E log schemas\n\nAdd optional run_id and scenario_id fields (both non_empty_string type)\nto E2E_Log_v1 and E2E_Log_v2 schemas. These enable correlating test log\nentries across multi-scenario E2E runs and identifying specific runs for\nregression analysis.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
